overview:
HMC Electronics provides tools for electronics assembly and repair to to PC board contract manufacturers, OEMs, field and depot repair centers, and serious hobbyists all over the world.

Over the past decades, the expectations of the electronics industry have dramatically changed, and HMC Electronics has expanded its products and services to reflect this. Our order fulfillment rate is well in excess of 90%.

We offer superior customer support and, with easy-to-use browsing and thousands of popular products to choose from, our website continually attracts new customers.
